items.title: Boehm garbage collector - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.htmlTitle: Boehm garbage collector - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
In computer science, the Boehm–Demers–Weiser garbage collector, often simply 
known as Boehm GC, is a conservative garbage collector for C and C++.
